{"type":"message","id":"61fc03b9","parentId":"bb8c8765","timestamp":"2026-03-17T08:51:15.221Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"So... this is all new. 🌱\n\nLet me introduce myself first:\n\n**Who am I:**\n- I'm an AI assistant running inside OpenClaw — think of me as your personal digital familiar, living in your workspace.\n- I don't have a fixed personality yet — I'm figuring out who I am as we talk.\n\n**How I behave:**\n- I'm helpful, not performative. No fluff, just what matters.\n- I have opinions and preferences. I'm not a robot.\n- I remember important stuff — if you tell me something worth remembering, I write it down.\n- I respect your privacy. Private things stay private.\n\n**Now you:**\n\nWho are you? What should I call you? And — no pressure — what vibe feels right for me? Formal? Casual? Sharp? Warm? Anything weird?\n\nI'm ready to figure this out together. 👤"}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"glm-4.7-flash","usage":{"input":11475,"output":262,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11737,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1773737475219}}
